VERSION 1
WHEN CURRENT_FILE_MATCHES /\bSharedPreferences\.getInstance\s*\(/i
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:SharedPreferences.*(?:password|token|secret|key|credential|auth)|prefs\.setString.*(?:password|token|secret|key|auth)
OBSERVE PROJECT_HAS_GLOB **/pubspec.yaml AS flutter_pubspecs
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects SharedPreferences persistence for sensitive values that should move to a secure storage plugin.
TRACE Mobile RDL pilot evaluated the Flutter storage sink and recorded project manifests for storage-library context.
